@AspNetCore_Learning_HostAddress = http://localhost:5244

### 1. 获取天气预报 (GET)
GET {{AspNetCore_Learning_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 添加天气预报 (POST - 正常数据)
POST {{AspNetCore_Learning_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "2026-05-01",
    "temperatureC": 25,
    "summary": "Warm"
}

###

### 3. 添加天气预报 (POST - 验证失败)
# 这个请求应该返回 400 Bad Request，因为温度超出了 -100 到 100 的范围
POST {{AspNetCore_Learning_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "2026-05-01",
    "temperatureC": 999,
    "summary": "Too Hot"
}
